snippet.title: YouTube LIVE with the Cavani String Quartet: Songs Without Words
snippet.description:
This event starts at 6pm, and occurs prior to ENCORE’s Blooming Artist Concert #1: ‘Songs Without Words’ at 7pm (https://www.encorechambermusic.org/livestream)

ENCORE’s String Quartet Intensive Program Directors, Cavani String Quartet, speak about the experience of teaching at ENCORE and the 2021 Season’s Young Artists Concert program, ‘Songs Without Words’.

Host: Jinjoo Cho, Artistic DirectorSpeakers: Cavani String Quartet, SQI Program Director
